ESSENTIAL METRICS DASHBOARD
Track weekly, review monthly: 
Growth metrics: 
MRR (absolute and growth rate) New signups this week AR (signups → activated) Conversion rate (activated → paying) 
Retention metrics: 
Monthly logo CR Monthly revenue CR Net revenue retention 
Economics metrics: 
CAC_BY_CHANNEL_LTV CAC ratio
Leading indicators (predict future revenue): 
Traffic to marketing site Trial starts Feature adoption rates Support ticket volume (rising = problems ahead) 
